                        <div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid">
                            <div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12">
                                <div class="vc_column-inner">
                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                        <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
                                            <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coronavirus has led to a number of propane events, conferences and trade shows being cancelled, as others are considering cancellation or are postponing to a later date.The Virtual Propane Expo (VPE) was created in response to the challenges that the Coronavirus has placed on our industry. </span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We launched our first show on April 29th and it was met with overwhelming success. In the first two weeks we had:</span></p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Over </span><b>400 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">registrants</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>3000 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">unique site visits</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>10 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">presenters</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>175 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">vendors</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>12 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Premium Sponsors were party to the first effort.</span></li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Additional VPE were held </span><b>May 28</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and participation is growing rapidly. As of June 10 2020, we expect VPE to be held at the end of June, July and beyond, typically at the end of each month.</span></p>
                                                <p><b>There was and is no cost to attendees </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">to virtually visit vendors or participate in any of the presentations.</span></p>
                                                <p><b>There was and is no cost to become a VPE “Media Partner”. See below for a summary on how to become a VPE Media Partner. </b></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As members of the VPE Advisory Board, we are proud to have been apart of this </span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ground- breaking event, that, in a matter of weeks from launch, was attended by hundreds of vendors and propane marketers. Feedback has been very positive. </span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We welcome your participation in future VPE activities, and would be pleased to have your publication or firm as a </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There is </span><b>no cost to your publication</b></p>
                                                <p><b>VPE will:</b></p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Promote your publication on the VPE website as an </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, including:</span>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Listing you in the </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> page at no cost</span></li>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Show your logo on the </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> page</span></li>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Include your name and logo on the </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Banner</span></li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Identify your publication on VPE communications to media, propane marketers and vendor communities as a </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Post your URL on www.virtualpropaneexpo.com</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide your publication with a VPE background and summary letter for use as you see fit</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide your publication with the option to present &#8211; or introduce speakers &#8211; at future VPE sessions on your choice of topics. Live or pre-recording presentations are welcome. Please, by all means, feel free to use your own educators and trainers</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide your publication with ready-to-use </span><b>VPE Media Partner </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">image files for your e-publications showing your publication a </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide your publication with a premium partner virtual booth for you to establish your company presence including logo, sales message and links to videos, brochures and sales pages all in the premier sponsor area.</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Virtual Propane Expo Intro: WIIFY &#8211; What’s In it For You. Provide your publication with Front &amp; Center placement of your short video speaking to your view on changes to the promotional tools available to the industry in the wake of Covid-19</span></li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <p><b>In return, VPE asks that your publication do any 2 (two) of the following:</b></p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Inform your propane community of VPE. </span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Add the link to VPE &#8211; </span><a href="https://virtualpropaneexpo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">www.virtualpropaneexpo.com</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to your publication website</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Add the link to VPE to your publication outgoing email signatures</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide VPE a space in your publication regular e-publications for VPE logo and its URL.</span></li>
                                                    <li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Include VPE in your digital marketing program</span></li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The above are just examples. Please let us know if you have any suggestions.</span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is an opportunity to provide value and continuity of communications to and with your readers by providing an easy-to-access forum for your readers to visit with marketers as well vendors about relevant topics. The list includes New Technologies to help grow their businesses, briefings on propane liability issues, safety, training and compliance challenges, and more. </span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These are certainly challenging times and they require outside-the-box thinking to address the needs of the propane industry in general and your readers.</span></p>
                                                <p><b>Please note that your publication is welcome to be </b><b>listed for free</b><b> even if you choose not to become a VPA Media Partner. Just use the Vendor Sign Up form link at the VPE home page</b></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you will join us as a </span><b>VPE Media Partner</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, simply reply in the affirmative, and we will get started</span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Thanks for your consideration.</span></p>
                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sincerely,</span></p>
